    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your own worst enemy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jobless, cashless, worthless. No network, no plans; only a free falling psyche and a cold smoking gun accompanies you now. How you handle the next few days will determine if there are any bright ones left to come.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283090/extras/66ff78ea4412a14f61af2192d587abcd.avif?t=1769473863\" width=600 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survival of the hopeful</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maintain a level head and fight a variety of terrible monsters as you stumble between nightmare and reality in this brooding first-person shooter. The road to recovery is long, so keep a sharp eye out for weapons, supplies and anything that might put a smile on your face. After all, bullets are no good when pointed the wrong way...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283090/extras/777113923c7952d83c64638049009b99.avif?t=1769473863\" width=600 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mix of linear and open levels with secrets to discover </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over a dozen enemy types including bosses</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reactive sanity system <i>(impacted by violence, self-care and more)</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable Horde Mode <i>(comes in three difficulties)</i></p></li></ul>",
